{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/2019/12/common-problems-in-using-gnuPg/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"4c32c915-582c-578e-bc79-d0deb052c6c9","html":"<!-- endExcerpt -->\n<p><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/GNU_Privacy_Guard\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">GNU Privacy Guard (GnuPG 或 GPG)</a> 是赛门铁克 <a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/PGP\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">PGP</a> 加密套件的自由软件替代品。</p>\n<p>关于 GPG(PGP) 有两则轶事。</p>\n<p>作者齐默尔曼差点因 PGP 的强加密功能而被指控为“没有授权的军需品出口”。军需品——枪支、炸药、飞机和软件的出口是被限制的，齐默尔曼就使用了一种富有想象力的方法来对抗这一规定。他将 PGP 的全套源代码出版成一本书，于是作为书本出口，受到<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E4%BF%AE%E6%AD%A3%E6%A1%88\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">第一修正案</a>的保护。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 470px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ecc1ff6eb4ffcbbe03fa23bddde95acf/65eb2/PGP_Source_Code_and_Internals.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 106.3157894736842%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/ecc1ff6eb4ffcbbe03fa23bddde95acf/5ed05/PGP_Source_Code_and_Internals.webp 190w,\n/static/ecc1ff6eb4ffcbbe03fa23bddde95acf/9d76b/PGP_Source_Code_and_Internals.webp 380w,\n/static/ecc1ff6eb4ffcbbe03fa23bddde95acf/d5ad8/PGP_Source_Code_and_Internals.webp 470w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 470px) 100vw, 470px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/ecc1ff6eb4ffcbbe03fa23bddde95acf/89129/PGP_Source_Code_and_Internals.jpg 190w,\n/static/ecc1ff6eb4ffcbbe03fa23bddde95acf/0036d/PGP_Source_Code_and_Internals.jpg 380w,\n/static/ecc1ff6eb4ffcbbe03fa23bddde95acf/65eb2/PGP_Source_Code_and_Internals.jpg 470w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 470px) 100vw, 470px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/ecc1ff6eb4ffcbbe03fa23bddde95acf/65eb2/PGP_Source_Code_and_Internals.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Book: PGP Source Code and Internals\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>另一则，在<a href=\"https://citizenfourfilm.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">纪录片《第四公民(Citizen Four)》</a>（<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/av24623314/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">在 BiliBili上观看</a>）画面中配有使用 GPG 解密消息的画面，Edward Snowden 就是通过 GPG 与记者进行加密通讯的。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 663px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8de1abea099742f32f576f8d81fa9b18/14bc7/citizen_four_gpg.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.263157894736835%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/8de1abea099742f32f576f8d81fa9b18/5ed05/citizen_four_gpg.webp 190w,\n/static/8de1abea099742f32f576f8d81fa9b18/9d76b/citizen_four_gpg.webp 380w,\n/static/8de1abea099742f32f576f8d81fa9b18/9946f/citizen_four_gpg.webp 663w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 663px) 100vw, 663px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/8de1abea099742f32f576f8d81fa9b18/253c6/citizen_four_gpg.png 190w,\n/static/8de1abea099742f32f576f8d81fa9b18/810ee/citizen_four_gpg.png 380w,\n/static/8de1abea099742f32f576f8d81fa9b18/14bc7/citizen_four_gpg.png 663w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 663px) 100vw, 663px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/8de1abea099742f32f576f8d81fa9b18/14bc7/citizen_four_gpg.png\"\n            alt=\"Using GPG decrypt message in documentary Citizen Four\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>下面记载一些使用 GPG 的教程与常见问题。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"通俗易懂的-gpg-教程\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E9%80%9A%E4%BF%97%E6%98%93%E6%87%82%E7%9A%84-gpg-%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B\" aria-label=\"通俗易懂的 gpg 教程 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>通俗易懂的 GPG 教程</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.ruanyifeng.com/blog/2013/07/gpg.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">GPG入门教程</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://vimacs.wehack.space/openpgp-about.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">从 keyserver 获取其他人的 GPG 公钥</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"最佳实践\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%B3%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5\" aria-label=\"最佳实践 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>最佳实践</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://oguya.ch/posts/2016-04-01-gpg-subkeys/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">GPG Subkeys</a> 的建议。使用子密钥，仅当需要如下情景时才用主密钥对：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>创建新子密钥</li>\n<li>改变一个 UID 的首选项</li>\n<li>吊销 UID 或 子密钥</li>\n<li>为密钥签名或撤销现有签名</li>\n<li>创建新的 UID 或将现有的 UID 标记为主要</li>\n<li>更改主密钥或其任何子密钥的过期日期</li>\n</ul>\n<p>请参考如下最佳实践文章：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://2xiangzi.blogspot.com/2016/09/perfect-gpg-keypair.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">如何创建完美的GPG密钥对</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/mdrights/Digital-rights/blob/master/T%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B%E5%92%8C%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/2019-04-17-OpenPGP-%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E7%AD%BE%E5%90%8D%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%B3%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5-Mailfence.md\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">OpenPGP 数字签名最佳实践</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://jackqqcn.wordpress.com/2008/06/22/gnupg-%E7%94%A8%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%AAsub-keys%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4primary-key/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">GnuPG: 用多个sub keys保护primary key</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://oguya.ch/posts/2016-04-01-gpg-subkeys/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">GPG Subkeys</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.tinned-software.net/create-gnupg-key-with-sub-keys-to-sign-encrypt-authenticate/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Create GnuPG key with sub-keys to sign, encrypt, authenticate</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"只能上传一个-subkey-到-keyserver\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%8F%AA%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%8A%E4%BC%A0%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA-subkey-%E5%88%B0-keyserver\" aria-label=\"只能上传一个 subkey 到 keyserver permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>只能上传一个 subkey 到 keyserver</h2>\n<p>有的 keyserver 只支持一个 subkey，在文章<a href=\"https://jackqqcn.wordpress.com/2008/06/22/gnupg-%E7%94%A8%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%AAsub-keys%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4primary-key/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">GnuPG: 用多个sub keys保护primary key</a>中有提及。</p>\n<h2 id=\"简便易用的-gui-for-gnupg\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%AE%80%E4%BE%BF%E6%98%93%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84-gui-for-gnupg\" aria-label=\"简便易用的 gui for gnupg permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>简便易用的 GUI for GnuPG</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>参见 <a href=\"https://www.gnupg.org/software/frontends.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">GnuPG Software Frontends</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"警告签名的子密钥--未经交叉验证\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E7%AD%BE%E5%90%8D%E7%9A%84%E5%AD%90%E5%AF%86%E9%92%A5--%E6%9C%AA%E7%BB%8F%E4%BA%A4%E5%8F%89%E9%AA%8C%E8%AF%81\" aria-label=\"警告签名的子密钥  未经交叉验证 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>警告：签名的子密钥 … 未经交叉验证</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">WARNING: signing subkey <span class=\"token punctuation\">..</span>. is not cross-certified</code></pre></div>\n<p>验证签名的警告，下面给出的链接有很清楚的<a href=\"https://gnupg.org/faq/subkey-cross-certify.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">解决方案与说明</a></p>","excerpt":"","fields":{"slug":"/2019/12/common-problems-in-using-gnuPg","categorySlugs":["/category/信息安全/"],"tagSlugs":["/tag/gnu-pg/","/tag/公钥加密/"]},"frontmatter":{"title":"使用 GnuPG 的常见问题","date":"2019-12-16T10:46:37.121Z","categories":["信息安全"],"description":"GnuPG 是赛门铁克 PGP 加密套件的自由软件替代品。记载一些使用 GPG 的教程与常见问题。","tags":["GnuPG","公钥加密"],"slug":"/2019/12/common-problems-in-using-gnuPg","featured_media":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"fixed","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/d42d71d85c658f84de931ceb7fbb0c26/e737e/featured_media.jpg","srcSet":"/static/d42d71d85c658f84de931ceb7fbb0c26/e737e/featured_media.jpg 800w","sizes":"800px"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/d42d71d85c658f84de931ceb7fbb0c26/e7773/featured_media.we